{"tid":1369212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真.元朗購物團","createTime":"2019-07-26T15:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T09:01:50.000Z","uid":276865,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2d9bae5281a36e1d8d4cf889331fdae1e245cd0","tid":1369212,"uid":276865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:51:22.000Z","msg":"如果聽日元朗發夢變咗購物團，一大堆人去買嘢，場面應該好震撼，一來受街坊商戶歡迎，二來凸顯白衣黑衣反差，破壞同建設，三來唔犯法，汪汪連拉人嘅藉口都冇，咁林奠同汪汪就輸到底褲都甩埋，民意就係要害，中到就贏。"},{"pid":"f474ca3b26b8e68541b4dc9fbf30832536c58204","tid":1369212,"uid":276865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e193e16bbf1f4bf6be24de77742b3d2671512f88","tid":1369212,"uid":267801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"將港島游行模式帶到元朗。"},{"pid":"808608202accc2096ec421a493b44405e13bfa0e","tid":1369212,"uid":276865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:00:50.000Z","msg":"大部分人嘅諗法先係最緊要，林奠輸到pk就係輸民意，先至有今日"},{"pid":"a354284090dd47d69e57ff321235d884bf9e8283","tid":1369212,"uid":36761,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m64n5cK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm64n5cK.jpg&h=434be3bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2c51b6849e50ad98e4398fff048f2ddcf4eb8c3","tid":1369212,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:05:04.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4c677c8eb643f9d713c37c2120199444b350f684","tid":1369212,"uid":276865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"要贏民心同冇得拉人"},{"pid":"c0